<p><a href="http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/0060599332/theworldofhalcan">Quicksilver: The Deluxe Limited Edition</a></p>
<blockquote><div>
<ul>
<li>Limited to an edition of 1,000 copies-never to be reprinted. </li>
<li>Completely redesigned from the trade hardcover in a larger format-7&quot; x 10&quot;.</li>
<li>Each book numbered and signed by the author. </li>
<li>Each volume hand-bound in Japanese silk. </li>
<li>Each volume housed in a handsome slipcase featuring a die-cut aperture for the Quicksilver icon and covered in the same Japanese silk. The slipcase will also feature a silk ribbon pull for easy removal. </li>
<li>Matching signed limited editions of the second and third volumes of Stephenson's Baroque Cycle will be published by William Morrow at six-month intervals.</li>
</ul>
